anacron (Anacron2)

Anacron is a periodic command scheduler. It executes commands
at intervals specified in days. Cron is useful with "always on"
server, anacron with desktop, notebook, and anything that you turn
off. The original anacron has been unmaintained since 2000.



HOME: http://sourceforge.net/projects/anacron2/

